OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FA woman has been found guilty of
OL,7,Ffatally cutting her film director
OL,8,Fsister in the neck before making off
OL,9,Fwith her diamond-encrusted gold Rolex
OL,10,Fwatch.
OL,12,FNancy Pexton slashed and stabbed her
OL,13,Fsibling Jennifer Abbott 10 times and
OL,14,Fthen left her body for three days in
OL,15,Fher flat in Camden, north London.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, an Old Bailey jury
OL,18,Fconvicted Pexton, 70, of murdering Ms
OL,19,FAbbott on June 10 last year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
