OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FUS citizen Ms Abbott, 69, was last
OL,7,Fseen alive on a doorbell camera as she
OL,8,Freturned from walking her corgi Prince
OL,9,Fat 7.36am that day.
OL,11,FPexton spoke to her by phone at
OL,12,F11.36am and travelled by bus to her
OL,13,FMornington Place flat at 12.45pm,
OL,14,Fleaving an hour later.
OL,16,FShe then called her GP, reported
OL,17,Ftaking an overdose and was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital where she stayed before her
OL,19,Farrest on June 18.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FOn June 13, a neighbour used a
OL,7,Fscaffolding pole to break down Ms
OL,8,FAbbott's door after becoming concerned
OL,9,Fhe could not hear her dog barking.
OL,11,FHer niece Mai Pexton had been seen
OL,12,Fbanging on the door and screaming for
OL,13,Fher "auntie".
OL,15,FMs Abbott's partially naked and
OL,16,Fdecomposing body was found on the
OL,17,Fliving room floor with gaffer tape
OL,18,Fover her mouth.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FShe had a large, gaping "slash-type"
OL,7,Fwound across her neck and gaffer tape
OL,8,Facross her mouth, jurors heard.
OL,10,FMs Abbott's corgi had been trapped in
OL,11,Fthe kitchen and was freed by
OL,12,Ffirefighters.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found Ms
OL,15,FAbbott had sustained a number of stab
OL,16,Fand slash wounds and a single
OL,17,Fdefensive wound to the right hand.
OL,19,FHer Rolex watch, a gift from her son
OL,20,FBrad Carlson which she never took off,
OL,21,Fwas missing.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FIt was later recovered by police from
OL,7,FPexton's bag after they visited her in
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FWhen quizzed about it, Pexton said she
OL,11,Fhad been given it to "look after".
OL,13,FHowever, prosecutor Bill Boyce KC
OL,14,Fsuggested Ms Abbott would never have
OL,15,Fgiven away her "prized Rolex watch".
OL,17,FHe told jurors: "The reality, of
OL,18,Fcourse, is that the defendant took the
OL,19,Fwatch having stabbed her sister to do
OL,20,Fso."
OL,26,@sD@VOUsD@aO]wD@POUwD@cO]yD@QOU|D@DO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FIn the two days after Ms Abbott's
OL,7,Fdeath, there were numerous missed
OL,8,Fcalls from her son Mr Carlson, who
OL,9,Flives abroad.
OL,11,FMr Carlson described a "bubbling"
OL,12,Fresentment between his mother and aunt.
OL,14,FGiving evidence via videolink, Mr
OL,15,FCarlson said: "There was interaction
OL,16,Fand sometimes anger and hostility
OL,17,Fbetween my mother and Nancy, there was
OL,18,Fresentment seemingly bubbling up.
OL,26,@sD@XOUsD@aO]wD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FJurors also heard how Ms Abbott told
OL,7,Fher nephew that she was scared for her
OL,8,Fsafety as Pexton was "capable of
OL,9,Fanything".
OL,11,FIn November 2024, she had shared a
OL,12,Fmessage in which Pexton told her: "You
OL,13,Fknow I was planning to kill you but it
OL,14,Fwas just a thought, I would never hurt
OL,15,Fyou."
OL,17,FThe message went on to warn Ms Abbott
OL,18,Fto "watch your back from those you
OL,19,Fconned and stole money from".
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@IO]tD@cOUwD@EO]zD@DOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FPexton wrote: "You never know they
OL,7,Fcould get you while you walking your
OL,8,Fdog. Be careful honey, I worry about
OL,9,Fyou. You so many enemy (sic)."
OL,11,FAt the time, Ms Abbott asked her
OL,12,Fnephew if she should take out a
OL,13,Frestraining order.
OL,15,FFurther evidence of Pexton's
OL,16,Fresentment were found in a series of
OL,17,Fnotes on her phone in which she
OL,18,Freferred to thinking about killing her
OL,19,F"evil" sister and complained about
OL,20,Fother family members.
OL,26,@nD@OOUqD@^O]{D@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FPexton later told police she had just
OL,7,Fbeing "venting" her feelings and that
OL,8,Fshe really loved her sister.
OL,10,FShe claimed to have no memory of the
OL,11,F90 minutes covering the time spent in
OL,12,Fher flat.
OL,14,FOn that day, she had been wearing a
OL,15,Fblack cowboy hat and blue dungarees
OL,16,Fwhich were covered in her sister's
OL,17,Fblood "from top to bottom".
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@OO]yD@GOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FJurors were told that Pexton had asked
OL,7,Fone of her daughters to take the
OL,8,Fclothes away and wash them or throw
OL,9,Fthem away.
OL,11,FThe defendant, who has two grown-up
OL,12,Fdaughters, went on to explain that the
OL,13,Fblood got on her clothes when she
OL,14,Fhugged her sister who had suffered a
OL,15,Fnosebleed.
OL,17,FBut Mr Boyce said scientific analysis
OL,18,Fdid not support her claim and
OL,19,Fsuggested Ms Abbott's blood went
OL,20,Feverywhere when Pexton slashed and cut
OL,21,Fher 10 times.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777468273
OL,3,CSister guilty of killing film director
OL,4,Csibling for Rolex watch
OL,6,FAn examination of Ms Abbott's flat
OL,7,Falso showed evidence that someone had
OL,8,Ftried to "clean up", he said.
OL,10,FPexton, of no fixed address, had
OL,11,Fdenied wrongdoing and declined to give
OL,12,Fevidence in her trial, opting to
OL,13,Fappear in court by videolink from
OL,14,FBronzefield jail.
OL,16,FFollowing the guilty verdict, Judge
OL,17,FAnuja Dhir KC adjourned sentencing to
OL,18,FFriday.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
